data.title: TN Companies PAN GST
data.meta_description: TN Companies PAN GST - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document appears to be a list of GST registrations with details including the GSTIN, legal name, and whether they are allocated to the Centre or State. It includes 83 entries of various organizations like cooperative societies, weavers associations, milk producers unions, lorry owners associations, and others that are all allocated to the Centre.
